\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/images/logo/logo-512.png\"}},\"about\":{\"@type\":\"City\",\"name\":\"Chesterfield, MO\"},\"mainEntity\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/chesterfield-mo#itemlist\"},\"containsPlace\":[{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/eberwein-dog-park-membership-required\",\"name\":\"Eberwein Dog Park (Membership Required)\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/eberwein-dog-park-membership-required\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://www.chesterfield.mo.us/eberwein-park.html\"],\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"streetAddress\":\"1627 Old Baxter Rd\",\"addressLocality\":\"Chesterfield\",\"addressRegion\":\"MO\",\"postalCode\":\"63017\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"telephone\":\"(636) 537-4000\",\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":4.2,\"reviewCount\":58},\"geo\":{\"@type\":\"GeoCoordinates\",\"latitude\":38.64228719999999,\"longitude\":-90.5646439}}]}25:T47f,{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where is the dog park in Chesterfield, MO?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"The Eberwein Dog Park is a community favorite, featuring fenced areas for different sized dogs. Note that it is available to residents only and requires a tag.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there public dog parks near Chesterfield?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, for non-residents, the nearby Quail Ridge Park in Wentzville or Broemmelsiek Park offer excellent off-leash areas that are open to the general public.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I hike with my dog in Chesterfield?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Absolutely. The Riparian Trail and the Monarch Levee Trail are popular paved options for leashed dog walking, winding through scenic wetland areas.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is Chesterfield Mall dog-friendly?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"While the mall interior policy can vary, individual stores and the surrounding retail developments often welcome pets. Always check signage before entering.\"}}]}19:[[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$24\"}}],[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ItemList\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/chesterfield-mo#itemlist\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks in Chesterfield\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Top-rated dog parks and facilities in Chesterfield, MO\\\",\\\"numberOfItems\\\":1,\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"item\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"SportsActivityLocation\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/eberwein-dog-park-membership-required\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Eberwein Dog Park (Membership Required)\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/eberwein-dog-park-membership-required\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Located in Chesterfield, Eberwein Dog Park (Membership Required) offers a welcoming space for pets to exercise and socialize.\\\\n\\\\nThis park is well-equipped with amenities such as indoor facilities for...\\\",\\\"address\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"PostalAddress\\\",\\\"addressLocality\\\":\\\"Chesterfield\\\",\\\"addressRegion\\\":\\\"MO\\\",\\\"addressCountry\\\":\\\"US\\\"}}}]}\"}}],[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$25\"}}],\"$L26\",\"$L27\",\"$L28\",\"$L29\",\"$L2a\",\"$L2b\"]\n2c:I[90491,[\"8500\",\"static/chunks/8500-98e13bcce54aa7a0.js\",\"7828\",\"static/chunks/7828-fd723da158040787.js\",\"2365\",\"st